casebody.data:
JOHN H. UPSHAW v. RENUART LUMBER YARDS, INC., Employer; Bituminous Casualty Corporation, Insurer; and Florida Industrial Commission. 9 So. (2nd) 806

June Term, 1942

October 2, 1942 Division B Rehearing Denied October 2, 1942 Knight & Green, for appellant. Leon Harvell, for appellees. PER CURIAM:

No error having been made clearly to appear the order of the circuit court affirming the one of the ■ industrial commission is—

Affirmed.

BROWN, C. J., TERRELL, CHAPMAN and THOMAS, JJ., concur.
